title: WhyQ Hawker Delivery & Marketplace

creator: WhyQ Pte. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
With WhyQ "Shiok", you can choose from over 3,000 hawker stalls, street food and small eateries; and order conveniently with low delivery fees.

WhyQ is Singapore’s largest food delivery service for small food businesses. We do not charge our vendors any commissions, or on-boarding fees, and we are able to provide same day payments,

WhyQ's in-house batch aggregation delivery model ensures your food remains fresh and your food delivery remains affordable.

Updates

On-demand deliveries
WhyQ now offers on-demand deliveries during our vendor operating hours. Simply choose "ASAP" delivery after selecting your favorite food stall!

WhyQ Premium
WhyQ now offers islandwide deliveries from our created list of most popular partners, refreshed every month. Head over to "WhyQ Premium" in WhyQ Shiok!

Marketplace at WhyQ
This is a vendor agnostic platform that enables you to order from any vendors who do not want to continue being charged high commissions from other food delivery players. This is an initiative in partnership with NTUC. Select "Marketplace @ WhyQ" your app homepage!

WhyQ is Singapore’s largest food delivery service for small food businesses. We do not charge our vendors any commissions, or on-boarding fees, and we are able to provide same day payments,

WhyQ's in-house batch aggregation delivery model ensures your food remains fresh and your food delivery remains affordable.

Updates

On-demand deliveries
WhyQ now offers on-demand deliveries during our vendor operating hours. Simply choose "ASAP" delivery after selecting your favorite food stall!

WhyQ Premium
WhyQ now offers islandwide deliveries from our created list of most popular partners, refreshed every month. Head over to "WhyQ Premium" in WhyQ Shiok!
descriptionShort: WhyQ: Affordable and delicious hawker food deliveries with no minimum order.
